<section class="hero">
  <span class="status"><span class="dot"></span>Open to work</span>
  <h1>Hi, I'm Sakshi &mdash; a product designer turning complex problems into calm, structured experiences.</h1>
  <p>Currently designing experiences at <a href="https://juspay.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="highlight">Juspay</a>. I believe that great design goes beyond interfaces, diving into intention &amp; detail makes the experience truly exceptional.</p>
  <p>Based in Bengaluru. Reach me at <a href="mailto:hello@sakshi.in">hello@sakshi.in</a>.</p>
</section>

<style>
  .hero { padding: var(--space-88) 0 var(--space-72); }
  h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-hero-heading);
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    line-height: var(--leading-heading);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-22);
  }
  p {
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-14);
  }
  p a {
    color: var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color var(--ease-default), border-color var(--ease-default);
  }
  p a:hover { color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); }
  p a.highlight { color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .status {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-14);
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-8);
    font-size: var(--text-md); color: var(--muted);
  }
  .dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    background: var(--success); border-radius: 50%;
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .dot::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--success);
    animation: dot-pulse 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
  }
  @keyframes dot-pulse {
    0%   { transform: scale(1);   opacity: 0.55; }
    70%  { transform: scale(2.6); opacity: 0; }
    100% { transform: scale(2.6); opacity: 0; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero { padding: var(--space-56) 0 var(--space-48); }
    h1 { font-size: 22px; }
  }
</style>
